major - general robert clive , 1st baron clive ,   ( 29 september 1725   – 22 november 1774 ) , also known as clive of india , commander - in-chief of british india , was a british officer and soldier of fortune who established the military and political supremacy of the east india company in bengal .

the 18th century : robert clive was one of the major architects of british power in this colony

